&ldquo;So, what&rsquo;s your New Year&rsquo;s resolution?&quot;_
&ldquo;I resolve to live life on purpose, to take control of my fate, to sieze each day as if it were my last. I will be reckless. I will be daring. I will be strong. I will challenge fate. I will defy the gods. Or I will die trying.&rdquo;
&ldquo;&hellip; Why can&rsquo;t you just quit smoking or go on a diet like ordinary people?
